title: Rescue at Twelve Lakes
description: A couple own a restaurant at a mountain resort. One day while the wife is hiking on a mountain trail, she runs into a man she learns is an ex-convict--and finds herself strangely attracted to him.

title: Miss Jeremy and the Bran Serjin
The Westerner
description: A sheriff is kidnapped by a gang of outlaws and forced to guide them to the border with Mexico.

title: Who's Been Sitting in My Chair?
description: A disc jockey who discovers that, whenever he is away, someone sits in his arm chair.

title: The Girl in the Bathing Suit
Banana Boat to Blanca Cay
description: A retired sea captain who lost his ship at sea is vindicated when the ship is raised, revealing a damaged propeller shaft.

title: The Great Wide World
description: Cora Gibbs lives in the Ozarks and can neither read nor write.

title: Perfect Likeness
description: An itinerant artist visits a bar and solves a love triangle by producing an idealized portrait of the waitress.
